# Conventional Commit Template
# <type>(<scope>): <description>
#
# Types:   feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, chore
# Scopes:  repo, category, dedup, cli, log, docs, ci, config
# Example: feat(repo): add anthropics/skills to K2
# Example: fix(dedup): handle duplicate names across categories
# Example: docs(readme): add category reference table
